vote.title: Authorize the ratification to pay outstanding invoices to the Hach Company for wastewater flowmeter monitoring services within the wastewater collection system for the effective management of the collection system which is extremely instrumental during rain events - Not to exceed $123,282.88 - Financing: Dallas Water Utilities Fund
